<h1><a href="/words/<%= @word.id %>"><b><%= @word.word %></b></a></h1>

<p>Did you make a mistake when you were inputting your word? That's okay! You can update it with the form below. Or if you don't want this word to be included in your list of Wonderful Words anymore, you can delete it with the "Delete Word" button.</p>

<form action="/words/<%= @word.id() %>" method="post">
  <input name="_method" type="hidden" value="patch">

  <label for="word"><%= "Update #{@word.word} to be:" %></label>
  <input id="word" name="word" type="text" required>

  <button type="submit">Update</button>
</form>

<form action="/words/<%= @word.id %>" method="post">
  <input name="_method" type="hidden" value="delete">

  <button type="submit">Delete Word</button>
</form>

